target: TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDRED_000_000<tab>やはり、先陣を切ってきたか、蛮族の英雄め……！

source:
TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDBLUE_000_001But in the end, they are only that─savages.
Now, let us be brief. His Radiance awaits.
target: TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDBLUE_000_001<tab>陛下の理想を理解せぬ愚者は、ここで始末するッ！

source: TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDRED_000_010<tab>We have served our purpose. Come, we shall withdraw for now.
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDRED_000_010クソッ……やはり殿下を退けただけのことはあるか……！
時間は稼げた、一時後退するッ！
